This fixture is a single-file Go module whose main function calls an
undeclared identifier. gopls reports an error-severity diagnostic for the
undeclared name, which the diagnostics integration test asserts on.

The integration test queries diagnostics for main.go and expects at least one
error-severity diagnostic.

